Cell["\<\
New unification theory: The coupling splitting of gravitation (Graviton spin 2)
give Leptons spin 1/2 and quarks spin 3/2:Lepton_spin+Quark_spin=Graviton_spin\
\>", "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9785171340670357`*^9, 3.9785172823240128`*^9}, {
  3.978517608636572*^9, 3.978517662745833*^9}, {3.978518478090564*^9, 
  3.978518484098064*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b8cba25e-cc70-4500-8910-\
03fa79e27cef"],

Cell["\<\
That splitting  is the SU(5) to U(1)*SU(2)*SU(3) standard model of physics\
\>", "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.978517519216819*^9, 
  3.978517597645177*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"d1a2fc17-aa20-46d4-abac-\
9101b1f90f23"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
The new theory explains the field splitting as being a Kaluza-Klein type 5d \
splitting
of the gravitational field into three parts as 
1) electromagnetic U(1) : photon spin 1
2) Weak field SU(2): Leptons,{e,mu,tau),spin 1/2
3) SU(3) :Colored Quarks :red 1/2,blue1/2,yellow 1/2:total spin 3/2\
\>", "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.978518031407714*^9, 
  3.978518389686833*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"858135ae-c6d9-4766-b543-\
18184f3f08b0"],

